Marcus Says in Talks on Filling S. Africa Deputy Governor Post

-- B y   M i k e   C o h e n
-- 
2011-10-12T09:18:12Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-12/marcus-says-in-talks-on-filling-s-africa-deputy-governor-post.html
South African Reserve Bank Governor
Gill Marcus said the central bank is in discussions with
President  Jacob Zuma  about filling a vacant deputy-governor
post.  Marcus was briefing lawmakers in  Cape Town  today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Mike Cohen in Cape Town at 
